{"tid":1565361,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國議員：美中關係陷低谷 合作才是出路","createTime":"2019-09-13T06:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T08:17:13.000Z","uid":61672,"like":2,"dislike":65,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"5b6c1a8a18572efb4643f1e84552eb274a935782","tid":1565361,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:15:11.000Z","msg":"美中關係近年來發生極大轉變。美國對華政策在美國國防部將中國定義為戰略競爭對手后越趨強硬。持續至今的美中貿易戰更是令世界兩大經濟體的關係陷入低谷。美國國會民主黨籍眾議員拉爾森（Rick Larsen）認為，美中聯繫緊密相互依賴，雙方應該保持競爭與合作關係：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「我們或許可以不把中國定義為戰略競爭對手，而是競爭合作對象。我們承認美國在某些領域直接與中國競爭，但美國同時應該在某些方面和中國進行合作。」<br />\n<br />\n拉爾森星期三在美國和平研究所（United States institute of Peace）舉辦的研討會上作出了以上表述。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6b1rzu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6b1rzu.jpg&h=a72f1493&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bannedbook.org/bnews/zh-tw/headline/20190912/1189737.html/amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bannedbook.org%2Fbnews%2Fzh-tw%2Fheadline%2F20190912%2F1189737.html%2Famp&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=516066c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bannedbook.org/bnews/zh-tw/headline/20190912/1189737.html/amp</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好鬆懈！！！！！！"},{"pid":"e1d021a8bf167dabff1f004e5621eeadd7c80858","tid":1565361,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:15:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div